    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Thy con-fes--sion of the one di-vine Faith showed thee to__ the Church to be a new Paul and a zeal-ot a-mong__ priests, O ho-ly__ one. The right-eous blood both of A--bel and Zach-a-ry with thee doth cry out to-geth--er un-to the__ Lord. Right-eous Fa-ther, in-ter-cede with Christ God in our be-half that His great mer-cy may be grant-ed un--to__ us. \n\nun--to__ us.____"
